channel.title: SaraPkScape Has Come To An End
channel.description:
SaraPkScape has come to a end. I have finally reached my goal. My goal was to... 1. get 300 or more players(finished got 389 players) 2. get 100k character files(finished i stopped counting until i got 100k of em) 3. make a new minigame called Dragon Hunting(finished infact i got over 100 players playing that minigame at once) i have more goals but i cant list them.
I know everybody has a special feeling about SaraPkScape ending well i will like to thanks this people helping me through out my server time.
Credits: K o(My first server player) i loot i(i used your great sources throught SaraPkScape) bluur(nice soure also used it too) the person who owns total war scape(forgot his name anyway i liked that source) owner julie(my co-owner) All of my fellow admins and mods(thanks for a nice time through out SaraPkScape I have more People but i will list them later
I will be making 2 more servers 1 is a project and 1 is a server the project is pest control isle(based on pest control) the server is uber server 3.0(based on real rs2) i will call people to come and help me with this project and server
